{"tid":2514291,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港電台台灣疫情速報：增8宗確診　明起禁曾往印度人士入境　台居民除外","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:00.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b9849d641a9d7fac6b8e0b3bc0469a2c89e5e58","tid":2514291,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:19:00.000Z","msg":"台灣新增8宗新型肺炎確診個案，其中一名患者屬於諾富特桃園機場飯店群組。<br />\n<br />\n因應印度的疫情急速惡化，當局宣布，明日起禁止14日內到過印度的人士人境，台灣居民可獲豁免，但他們入境後仍要集中檢疫14日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588987-20210503.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588987-20210503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=7b2660fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588987-20210503.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=713fcec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588987-20210503.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}